{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/hacker-reviews.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>With Hacker Reviews, you have the option to send comments on hacker behavior to HackerOne and the hacker after closing a report. The reviews also enable the reviewer to highlight a key behavior which can allow HackerOne to award or assist the hacker accordingly.</p>\n<p>When giving a review, you can:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Choose whether to provide a positive or negative rating for the hacker.</li>\n<li>Select 1 of 4 preselected areas where the hacker excelled.</li>\n<li>Provide feedback to hackers and HackerOne about hacker behavior.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"enable-hacker-reviews\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#enable-hacker-reviews\" aria-label=\"enable hacker reviews permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Enable Hacker Reviews</h3>\n<p>To enable hacker reviews:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Program Settings > Program > Automation > Hackbot</strong>.</li>\n<li>Select <strong>Turn on</strong> for <em>Review reporter</em>.</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"how-reviews-work\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how-reviews-work\" aria-label=\"how reviews work permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How Reviews Work</h3>\n<p>To give a hacker review:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Close the report and mark as resolved.</li>\n<li>\n<p>Hackbot will prompt you to give the hacker of the report a review. You can choose from:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Yes, it was great!</li>\n<li>Could have been better.</li>\n<li>No thanks!\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.599999999999994%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hacker-review-1\"\n        title=\"hacker-review-1\"\n        src=\"/static/2362dde0b7841ae2c2c1e6f03f96973b/0b533/hacker-review-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2362dde0b7841ae2c2c1e6f03f96973b/fac75/hacker-review-1.png 125w,\n/static/2362dde0b7841ae2c2c1e6f03f96973b/63868/hacker-review-1.png 250w,\n/static/2362dde0b7841ae2c2c1e6f03f96973b/0b533/hacker-review-1.png 500w,\n/static/2362dde0b7841ae2c2c1e6f03f96973b/1d69c/hacker-review-1.png 750w,\n/static/2362dde0b7841ae2c2c1e6f03f96973b/00d43/hacker-review-1.png 1000w,\n/static/2362dde0b7841ae2c2c1e6f03f96973b/df438/hacker-review-1.png 1556w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>You'll fill out these forms if you choose to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Give a positive review\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hacker-review-2\"\n        title=\"hacker-review-2\"\n        src=\"/static/e9f5223592dd8e233b206e15eb5f71a7/0b533/hacker-review-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e9f5223592dd8e233b206e15eb5f71a7/fac75/hacker-review-2.png 125w,\n/static/e9f5223592dd8e233b206e15eb5f71a7/63868/hacker-review-2.png 250w,\n/static/e9f5223592dd8e233b206e15eb5f71a7/0b533/hacker-review-2.png 500w,\n/static/e9f5223592dd8e233b206e15eb5f71a7/1d69c/hacker-review-2.png 750w,\n/static/e9f5223592dd8e233b206e15eb5f71a7/00d43/hacker-review-2.png 1000w,\n/static/e9f5223592dd8e233b206e15eb5f71a7/4a00e/hacker-review-2.png 1406w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>Give a negative review\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hacker-review-3\"\n        title=\"hacker-review-3\"\n        src=\"/static/6bbb3ba754b38d393d7a941c746f79c3/0b533/hacker-review-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6bbb3ba754b38d393d7a941c746f79c3/fac75/hacker-review-3.png 125w,\n/static/6bbb3ba754b38d393d7a941c746f79c3/63868/hacker-review-3.png 250w,\n/static/6bbb3ba754b38d393d7a941c746f79c3/0b533/hacker-review-3.png 500w,\n/static/6bbb3ba754b38d393d7a941c746f79c3/1d69c/hacker-review-3.png 750w,\n/static/6bbb3ba754b38d393d7a941c746f79c3/00d43/hacker-review-3.png 1000w,\n/static/6bbb3ba754b38d393d7a941c746f79c3/67a79/hacker-review-3.png 1408w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Regardless of whether the review is positive or negative, the hacker will receive an email with the contents of the review.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hacker-review-4\"\n        title=\"hacker-review-4\"\n        src=\"/static/78c94804762c93083da1ef7ac01c2ea6/0b533/hacker-review-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/78c94804762c93083da1ef7ac01c2ea6/fac75/hacker-review-4.png 125w,\n/static/78c94804762c93083da1ef7ac01c2ea6/63868/hacker-review-4.png 250w,\n/static/78c94804762c93083da1ef7ac01c2ea6/0b533/hacker-review-4.png 500w,\n/static/78c94804762c93083da1ef7ac01c2ea6/1d69c/hacker-review-4.png 750w,\n/static/78c94804762c93083da1ef7ac01c2ea6/00d43/hacker-review-4.png 1000w,\n/static/78c94804762c93083da1ef7ac01c2ea6/8b70b/hacker-review-4.png 1266w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>When the review is positive, the reviewer also has the option to leave a public endorsement on the hacker's profile page, which serves as an opportunity to tell the world about just how awesome the hacker is.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 280px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hacker-review-5\"\n        title=\"hacker-review-5\"\n        src=\"/static/c5bdfc4762cc810d1868683796b68c24/908b1/hacker-review-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c5bdfc4762cc810d1868683796b68c24/fac75/hacker-review-5.png 125w,\n/static/c5bdfc4762cc810d1868683796b68c24/63868/hacker-review-5.png 250w,\n/static/c5bdfc4762cc810d1868683796b68c24/908b1/hacker-review-5.png 280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 280px) 100vw, 280px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/programs/hacker-reviews.html","id":"programs/hacker-reviews","title":"Hacker Reviews","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"Enable Hacker Reviews"},{"value":"How Reviews Work"}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}